<p>
<note n="0051001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0051001">本文 dhajaṁ ubhopiyaṁ 是 dhajaṁ ussāpitaṁ？</note>
<note n="0051002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0051002">本文 ca samāgate 是 ca samāgata？</note>
<note n="0051003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0051003">本文 pavattayī 是 pavattayim？</note>
<note n="0052004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052004">本文 saṁghassa tesu vihāraṁ 是 saṁghassa phāsuvihāraṁ。</note>
<note n="0052005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052005">本文 sāsanaṁ 是 sāsae？</note>
<note n="0052006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052006">本文 sutva 是 ñatvā？</note>
<note n="0052007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052007">本文 jātam anvayaṁ 是 jāta-m-anvayam？</note>
<note n="0052008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052008">本文 cejetvāna 是 cajitvāna？</note>
<note n="0052009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052009">本文 theravādo 是 theravāde？</note>
<note n="0052010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052010">本文 Asokassâbhisittato chasaṭṭhi Moggalisavhāyo 是 Asokâbhisitte chavasse saṭṭhi M？</note>
<note n="0052011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0052011">本文 sabbaṁ sutapariyattiṁ 是 sabba-ṁ-sutapariyatti？</note>
<note n="0054012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0054012">本文 vassānichattiṁsati 是 vassāni ca chattiṁsati？</note>
<note n="0054013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0054013">本文 yajā ekaṁ 是 pūjaṁ ekaṁ？</note>
<note n="0054014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0054014">本文 ekasmiṁ 是 etasmiṁ？</note>
<note n="0054015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0054015">本文 theyyasaṁvāsabhikkhuno 是 bhikkhūnam？</note>
</p>
